{"tid":463040,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[異地戀]好掛住我男朋友","createTime":"2017-11-09T06:30:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-10T09:47:37.000Z","uid":10254,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"89ef9f2d35c7e59357aaa7809febae29c1566ded","tid":463040,"uid":10254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T06:30:23.000Z","msg":"每日隔住個電話見好唔真實好痛苦 <br />\n返到香港屌到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 爆為止<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n等我阿"},{"pid":"b1aeafa14dfa71e8e960d70dcd48e36cc0f5a031","tid":463040,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T06:43:33.000Z","msg":"哈哈哈哈哈"},{"pid":"ffe3df39be78fe9b30b3027cf7288631cf8d88f7","tid":463040,"uid":77588,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T09:41:39.000Z","msg":"我同你個情況一樣，我女朋友都唔係香港一段時間<br />\n好掛住佢，好想攬下佢，錫下佢<br />\n好明你個感受，雖然我都覺得好辛苦<br />\n不過我懷住昐望一直等見到佢，我相信見到佢個刻，大家都會比以前更加無比咁珍惜對方，因為兩個人又跨過一個風浪，經歷左更多野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nsor for 1999"},{"pid":"0fda9ea0d7329e68a3ad77147adc62bd79de4405","tid":463040,"uid":10254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T09:54:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>哈哈哈哈哈</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6f5467a63982aa619dec57388336a2f6ab196d2","tid":463040,"uid":10254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T09:55:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我同你個情況一樣，我女朋友都唔係香港一段時間<br />\n好掛住佢，好想攬下佢，錫下佢<br />\n好明你個感受，雖然我都覺得好辛苦<br />\n不過我懷住昐望一直等見到佢，我相信見到佢個刻，大家都會比以前更加無比咁珍惜對方，因為兩個人又跨