"},{"pid":"3d09a9aabcc5c091b8739e1690f6324715f0b466","tid":463040,"uid":10254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T10:02:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>過多幾個月你就會出去偷食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n莫非你都有經驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n分隔兩地各自搵食是常識吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔會架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75778dcd5d9220d1bd6903422ab64ad2ce476cd7","tid":463040,"uid":31726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T10:05:36.000Z","msg":"我都好掛住我男朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf651c4e0101a4d7890c24e17b4dfdb9f5ff5606","tid":463040,"uid":10254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T10:09:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都好掛住我男朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> longd?"},{"pid":"8e3cc821117c2d5bd0c4c86b2df11a0047d59d3d","tid":463040,"uid":31726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T10:11:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我都好掛住我男朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> longd?</blockquote><br />\n係啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過12月會返香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f43b4a53a13e9fe5c99fadcf2d792ea5a86fcf6a","tid":463040,"uid":10254,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T10:13:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我都好掛住我男朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> longd?</blockquote><br />\n係啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過12月會返香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n等呢段日子好辛苦 雖然好快就到 但每一日都好似好耐咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8faf0c37f6e7eb38067587466f661168ac9f0a7","tid":463040,"uid":92496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T10:38:57.000Z","msg":"就黎有得翻香港見女朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"788e3c43fefb83d68054bd8ef6dfc1c3de3d4703","tid":463040,"uid":152633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T10:44:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>過多幾個月你就會出去偷食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n岩呀 通常longd都好易散 有幾多對情侶涯得過異地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6489df128caaf395b46734770feb820f986ccb60","tid":463040,"uid":58046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T10:47:45.000Z","msg":"this"},{"pid":"6c46a53766561f9eb814ad3f036742dcf378f3db","tid":463040,"uid":10254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T12:17:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>過多幾個月你就會出去偷食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n岩呀 通常longd都好易散 有幾多對情侶涯得過異地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係啊好多都捱唔過 唔計出軌 好多等唔到/接受唔到對方走就亂諗"},{"pid":"ac16bfd1c0c7bcea3a9e7da51ba5da4fb3e4aac5","tid":463040,"uid":10254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T12:17:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>就黎有得翻香港見女朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n恭喜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19190183ff65cfb811d8a0dfc706a39db3754d63","tid":463040,"uid":69177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T12:22:36.000Z","msg":"其實安全感先係最大問題"},{"pid":"ba2c361423adb9b9dcce7f5d1761615c3ebbc3dc","tid":463040,"uid":10254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T13:08:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實安全感先係最大問題</blockquote><br />\n係啊始終見唔到感覺有啲虛無"},{"pid":"2b66729f2676e41cc889b3e89f402a744e624341","tid":463040,"uid":120722,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T02:08:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>過多幾個月你就會出去偷食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n岩呀 通常longd都好易散 有幾多對情侶涯得過異地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我等左就快年半了。一開始等都仲可以，但近呢2個月我發現佢變左。無甘主動揾我，我吵又吵過了，哄又哄過了。結果都係甘。唉，我都唔知仲捱唔捱得過果半年，想見佢，佢唔理我。打比佢又唔听電話，情願出去玩都唔理我。我都唔知可以點，下個月飛去揾佢啦。我好驚佢會no show。"},{"pid":"e0296a00734821f26919d66931a189bfd6634a49","tid":463040,"uid":152633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T08:40:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>過多幾個月你就會出去偷食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n岩呀 通常longd都好易散 有幾多對情侶涯得過異地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我等左就快年半了。一開始等都仲可以，但近呢2個月我發現佢變左。無甘主動揾我，我吵又吵過了，哄又哄過了。結果都係甘。唉，我都唔知仲捱唔捱得過果半年，想見佢，佢唔理我。打比佢又唔听電話，情願出去玩都唔理我。我都唔知可以點，下個月飛去揾佢啦。我好驚佢會no show。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我之前一開始都係咁 初頭都好地地 大家都會日日傾電話 由日日傾 變左一星期一次 一個月一次 甚至無再傾電話 唔知係咪對方始終係個邊的生活比較新鮮 所以佢都涯唔住寂寞就搵左第二個分左手 <br />\n相信你地應該係經歷緊冷淡期 希望你飛過去搵佢個時可以有返以前熱戀期 加油 祝福你！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a35c9a875c51d87729000f5137f347e8b800d40","tid":463040,"uid":10254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T09:47:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>過多幾個月你就會出去偷食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n岩呀 通常longd都好易散 有幾多對情侶涯得過異地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我等左就快年半了。一開始等都仲可以，但近呢2個月我發現佢變左。無甘主動揾我，我吵又吵過了，哄又哄過了。結果都係甘。唉，我都唔知仲捱唔捱得過果半年，想見佢，佢唔理我。打比佢又唔听電話，情願出去玩都唔理我。我都唔知可以點，下個月飛去揾佢啦。我好驚佢會no show。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我之前一開始都係咁 初頭都好地地 大家都會日日傾電話 由日日傾 變左一星期一次 一個月一次 甚至無再傾電話 唔知係咪對方始終係個邊的生活比較新鮮 所以佢都涯唔住寂寞就搵左第二個分左手 <br />\n相信你地應該係經歷緊冷淡期 希望你飛過去搵佢個時可以有返以前熱戀期 加油 祝福你！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n下個會更好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}